		<div class="hotnews">
Our annual user conference, <a href="http://research.cs.wisc.edu/htcondor/HTCondorWeek2014/index.html">HTCondor
	Week</a> is scheduled for April 28-30, 2014</a>.  Save the date!
		</div>

